-- Ochocinco's Gold Shoes, Scott's Unsnapped Straps Draw $20,000 NFL Fines
-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 2010-11-13T04:04:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-13/ochocinco-s-gold-shoes-scott-s-unsnapped-straps-draw-20-000-nfl-fines.html
Cincinnati Bengals wide receiver
 Chad Ochocinco ’s golden football cleats cost him a $20,000 fine,
the National Football League said.  New York Jets linebacker  Bart Scott  also was fined $20,000
for violating the league’s uniform policy by neglecting to snap
his chin straps during the team’s 23-20 overtime victory Nov. 7
at Detroit.  Ochocinco wore his gold shoes, a violation of uniform
regulations, during the Bengals’ 27-21 loss to host Pittsburgh
on Nov. 8.  To contact the reporter on this story:
